      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LIGHT MY FIRE (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing eighth (20.34) last time in a Grade 5 at Muswellbrook. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Tough to beat if on-song. LEKTRA BELLA (2) ran good time (19.71) winning a Grade 5 three back at this track but missed the frame latest finishing eighth at this track. Expected to bounce back to best. NICMAC STAR (7) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (20.12) in a Grade 5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Can do much better this time. MOTOR CITY HAWK (8) is worth consideration.",
